.Ip "\(bu" 2
\f(CW$vector->Delete($offset,$bits);\fR
.Sp
This method deletes, i.e., removes the bits starting at position
\*(L"\f(CW$offset\fR\*(R" up to and including bit number \*(L"\f(CW$offset+$bits-1\fR\*(R"
