and \*(L"\f(CW$vec2\fR\*(R" may be identical.
.Ip "\(bu" 2
\f(CW$carry = $vec3->add($vec1,$vec2,$carry);\fR
.Sp
\f(CW($carry,$overflow) = $vec3->add($vec1,$vec2,$carry);\fR
.Sp
This method adds the two numbers contained in bit vector \*(L"\f(CW$vec1\fR\*(R"
and \*(L"\f(CW$vec2\fR\*(R" with carry \*(L"\f(CW$carry\fR\*(R" and stores the result in
