result if the number contained in bit vector \*(L"\f(CW$vec1\fR\*(R" is \f(CW2 ^ (n-1)\fR
(i.e., \*(L"1000...0000"), where \*(L"\f(CWn\fR\*(R" is the number of bits the given bit
