.Ip "\(bu" 2
\f(CW$sign = $vector->Sign();\fR
.Sp
This method returns \*(L"\f(CW0\fR\*(R" if all bits in the given bit vector are cleared,
i.e., if the given bit vector contains the number \*(L"\f(CW0\fR\*(R", or if the given
